 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Chlorophyll:

    This Pokémon's Speed is doubled 
  during strong sunlight.

  This bonus does not count as 
  a stat modifier.

  Leaf-guard:

    This Pokémon cannot be given 
  a major status ailment during 
  strong sunlight.

  This ability does not heal 
  prior status ailments. rest will 
  fail altogether with this ability 
  in effect. yawn will immediately 
  fail if used on this Pokémon 
  during strong sunlight, and an 
  already-used Yawn will fail if 
  the weather turns to strong sunlight 
  in the meantime.

  Infiltrator:

    This Pokémon's moves ignore 
  light screen, reflect, and safeguard.


